                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17250115-68-off360 t17250115-68-cd361"></join> last, between Seven and Eight at Night, William Green (followed by several others) came into his House, and said, G - D - my Body, you are my Prisoner. They carry'd him to <placeName id="t17250115-68-crimeloc362">the Sun at Green-Bank in the New Mint</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17250115-68-crimeloc362" type="placeName" value="the Sun at Green-Bank in the New Mint"></interp>
